  "html": "<p class=\"\">During the early COVID-19 pandemic, I worked with Carnegie Mellon University's <a href=\"https://delphi.cmu.edu/epidemic-signals/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\" data-preview-url=\"https://delphi.cmu.edu/epidemic-signals/\">COVIDcast project</a>, prototyping data visualizations and user interactions to help the public understand hospitalization, transmission, and movement trends across the country.</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p><figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Population density map of the United States with circles sized by population, colored white to red indicating concentration in the Midwest and Northeast.\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1755099710/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.41.38_AM.png\" alt=\"Population density map of the United States with circles sized by population, colored white to red indicating concentration in the Midwest and Northeast.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1755099710/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.41.38_AM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1755099710/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.41.38_AM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1755099710/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.41.38_AM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1755099710/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.41.38_AM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Population density map of the United States with circles sized by population, colored white to red indicating concentration in the Midwest and Northeast.\" style=\"background-color:#222222;background-image:url(&#x22;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%